        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued June 22 at 5:40PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 540 PM CDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm over
Nara Visa, moving northeast at 35 mph.

HAZARD...Wind gusts up to 50 mph.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects.

Locations impacted include...
Romero.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
